[{"id":"f7032369378fddd24f813a5faf10c49a","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"FW: For Jeffrey..","date":"2008-02-12T19:22:05.000Z","formatted_date":"Feb 12, 2008","formatted_time":"7:22 PM","body":" \n\n \n\nFrom: BEHNBOM@aol.com [mailto:BEHNBOM@aol.com] \nSent: Tuesday, February 12, 2008 2:16 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: For Jeffrey..\n\n \n\nDear Jeffrey,\n\n \n\nThis is our newest BBB in Stockholm, Freja Langert, very young, 21, but\nquite self-assured and smart - and sweet. She will be working with me\nthis year organizing our Swedish American Life Science Summit in\nStockholm this coming August. I will meet her at a big Swedish Health\nCare Summit in Wahington next week, she could come with me back to NYC\nnext weekend and perhaps stay the week here in NYC before going back;\nany chance she could stay at 301 E 66St?\n\nHope you are doing ok let me know if you will be around town.\n\n \n\nBig Hug,\n\n \n\nBarbro\n\n \n\n \n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n________________________________\n\nThe year's hottest artists on the red carpet at the Grammy Awards. AOL\nMusic takes you there.\n<http://music.aol.com/grammys?NCID=aolcmp00300000002565> \n\n","body_html":"<html xmlns:v=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:vml\" xmlns:o=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office\" xmlns:w=\"urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:word\" xmlns:m=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/2004/12/omml\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40\">\n\n<head>\n<META HTTP-EQUIV=\"Content-Type\" CONTENT=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<meta name=Generator content=\"Microsoft Word 12 (filtered medium)\">\n<!--[if !mso]>\n<style>\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\nw\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\n</style>\n<![endif]-->\n<style>\n<!--\n /* Font Definitions */\n @font-face\n\t{font-family:Calibri;\n\tpanose-1:2 15 5 2 