s-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Dear Jeffrey,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>This is our newest BBB in Stockholm, Freja Langert, very young,\n21, but quite self-assured and smart - and sweet. She will be working with me\nthis year organizing our Swedish American Life Science Summit in Stockholm this\ncoming August. I will meet her at a big Swedish Health Care Summit in Wahington\nnext week, she could come with me back to NYC next weekend and perhaps stay the\nweek here in NYC before going back; any chance she could stay at 301 E 66St?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Hope you are doing ok let me know if you will be around town.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Big Hug,<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>Barbro<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'>&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><img width=188 height=307 id=MA1.1202843741\nsrc=\"data:image/jpeg;base64,\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt'><span style='font-size:14.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'><br>\n<br>\n<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<div>\n\n<div class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:7.5pt;text-align:center'><span\nstyle='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>\n\n<hr size=2 width=\"100%\" align=center>\n\n</span></div>\n\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:7.5pt'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;\nfont-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";color:black'>The year's hottest artists on the\nred carpet at the Grammy Awards. <a\nhref=\"http://music.aol.com/grammys?NCID=aolcmp00300000002565\" target=\"_blank\"\ntitle=\"http://music.aol.com/grammys?NCID=aolcmp00300000002565\">AOL Music takes\nyou there.</a></span><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:\"Arial\",\"sans-serif\";\ncolor:black'><o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n</body>\n\n</html>\n","is_from_epstein":false,"attachments":1,"avatar_color":"#0f9d58","stars":6,"is_redacted":false}]